{
  "stem": "8916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I had-- I had good-- people didn't treat me badly and-- as a-- as a child--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--not especially.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In special barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there were-- there were barracks for men and barracks for women in the same camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, as-- as strange as it sounds, there-- they were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were people who practiced their religion, who celebrated the holidays.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As-- as hard as it was and as dangerous as it was, it was done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, occasionally they would.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they-- if they saw it, it was a very risky thing to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all done in--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Yom Kippur and Rosh Hashanah was-- was something I can remember as being kept.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In some-- in some-- in some quarters, in some situations, the sabbath.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those people who were-- who were older than I who had practiced their religion before the war had gotten-- got together and had prayer meetings and so on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't, but--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--my father would, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was always risky to do anything spiritual, whether it's singing songs or writing poems or-- or telling jokes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did all of those things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think that's part of resisting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, resisting isn't always with mechanical weapons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The facts are really that the Germans were conducting a war against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had a special army to do this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A special army that was equipped and had special marching orders.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- their job was to kill Jews, to murder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we resisted and fought back with all the-- the equipment we had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had men, women, and children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So naturally, the-- the odds were against us, and we took a lot of casualties, of course.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
